elements.name: Create a temporary placement for Weekly-Hours with funding type as Funded and funding model as Direct, reviewed and approved by internal users on behalf of external users

steps.name: login as Onboarding agent Maker user
navigate to the temporary placement list page
temporary placement details
select the funding type "Funded" in temporary placement form
select the currency in the temporary placement form
select the "Direct" model agency in the temporary placement form
select the "Direct" model client in the temporary placement form
select the "Direct" model contractor in the temporary placement form
fill the placement details in the temporary placement form
select the "Weekly" frequency in the temporary placement form
fill the standard rate details according to the unit type-"Hours" in the temporary placement form
Add the Additional rate according to the unit type-"Hours" in the temporary placement form, if required
Submit the temporary placement for Agency Approval
upload the Proof for Agency Approval-Rejection for the temporary placement
Approve the temporary placement on behalf of Agency user
upload the Proof for Client Approval-Rejection for the temporary placement
Approve the temporary placement on behalf of Client user
upload the Proof for Contractor Approval-Rejection for the temporary placement
Accept the temporary placement on behalf of Contractor user
"Weekly"-"Hours" Timesheets should get autogenerated for the "Direct" model maped entites with funding type as "Funded"
